{"tha-ap445:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap445:0.2":"Vibhitakavagga ","tha-ap445:0.3":"3 Billiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap445:1.1":"“Candabhaganaditire, ","tha-ap445:1.2":"assamo sukato mama; ","tha-ap445:1.3":"Billarukkhehi akinno, ","tha-ap445:1.4":"nanadumanisevito. ","tha-ap445:2.1":"Sugandham beluvam disva, ","tha-ap445:2.2":"buddhasetthamanussarim; ","tha-ap445:2.3":"Kharibharam purayitva, ","tha-ap445:2.4":"tuttho samviggamanaso. ","tha-ap445:3.1":"Kakusandham upagamma, ","tha-ap445:3.2":"billapakkamadasaham; ","tha-ap445:3.3":"Punnakkhettassa virassa, ","tha-ap445:3.4":"vippasannena cetasa. ","tha-ap445:4.1":"Imasmimyeva kappasmim, ","tha-ap445:4.2":"yam phalamadadim tada; ","tha-ap445:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap445:4.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap445:5.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap445:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap445:5.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap445:6.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap445:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap445:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap445:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap445:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap445:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap445:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma billiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap445:9.1":"Billiyattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}